** install requirement in main folder
pip install django djangorestframework django-cors-headers

** create a new django project for backend
django-admin startproject backend
cd backend/
python manage.py startapp api

** create a react project for frontend
npm create vite@latest frontend
cd frontend
npm i




** start backend server 

cd backend
python manage.py runserver 


** start frontend server 

cd frontend 
npm run dev 



cors : middleware (a fuction that exeucute before page load )



axios : a package used to create api, that will connect backend from frontend 

rest api methods
    post     : send data in to backend / database 
    get      : get data from backend / database 
    put      : update data in backend / database 
    delete   :  data in backend / database 


request :
    http://flipkart.com , http://localhost:5173 , 
     http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/demo = http://localhost:8000/api/demo  ---> server / backend --> respone --> view on html page




front-end : create account ,  login  --->  filling details -->  backend --->  database 